---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { url } from "../config";
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
    <div class="pb-12 mt-5">
        <img src={url('favicon.svg')} alt="" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" />
        <div class="text-xl py-1">
            Hey! you are under my watch! Be careful what you do here!
        </div>
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold">I'm Selene</div>
        <div class="text-xl py-6">
            I study machine learning systems, collect good questions, and turn
            messy ideas into little working things. <br />
            This is my corner for projects, notes, and whatever I am curious
            enough to chase next.
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-3">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold">Font sample</div>
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold">EN:</span> The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. 0123456789
            </div>
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold">简体:</span> 春眠不觉晓，处处闻啼鸟。夜来风雨声，花落知多少。
            </div>
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold">繁體:</span> 人生若只如初見，何事秋風悲畫扇。
            </div>
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold">日本語:</span> いろはにほへと ちりぬるを — 吾輩は猫である。名前はまだ無い。
            </div>
            <div class="text-lg">
                <span class="font-bold">한국어:</span> 다람쥐 헌 쳇바퀴에 타고파. 동해 물과 백두산이.
            </div>
            <div class="text-lg pt-6">
                2026 年 4 月，用 Astro v4.0 搭配 HarmonyOS Sans SC 与 Nunito Variable，实现 CJK + Latin 无缝 fallback —— 只要 <code>@font-face</code> 不用 <code>local()</code>。
                <code># 代码块字体使用 maple-mono-cn</code>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
